{"tid":1080920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公主病？港女趁男友瞓覺偷碌卡　網民勸分手","createTime":"2019-03-28T02:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T07:47:30.000Z","uid":225464,"like":10,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"27b2dab495af349af731ce2c6f1464d11ad4c1fb","tid":1080920,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:38:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>公主病？港女趁男友瞓覺偷碌卡 網民勸分手</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WrYh8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WrYh8b&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=82d9856f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WrYh8b</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190328/photo/bkn-20190328081515387-0328_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190328081817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190328081515387-0328_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190328081817&h=8cecfa21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當人男朋友定提款機呀？<br />\n<br />\n惡人先告狀？近日有港女疑偷用男友信用卡網購，並欲登入銀行手機程式刪除交易紀錄，不料多次登錄失敗遭到封鎖。一錯再錯的該名港女決定反斥男友不是，令網民大呼離譜！<br />\n<br />\n有港女投稿至Facebook專頁「十萬個激嬲女友的理由」，講述自己趁男友進入夢鄉時，偷偷地使用他的信用卡網購。為了神不知鬼不覺，她完事後欲登入男友的銀行手機程式刪除交易紀錄，並以自己的生日、二人的相識紀念日和拍拖紀念日，嘗試登入程式，豈料皆告失敗，更被程式封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n事後，男友嘗試登入該手機程式時揭發事件，該港女「見紙包唔住火」，決定先發制人，自行「爆大鑊」兼反咬男友一口：「我搶先嬲佢唔用我生日／紀念日做密碼，佢到依家都未氹得番我」。字裏行間，洋洋得意。<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，大批網友不值其所為而怒斥：「黐X線，打三條九拉佢啦」、「點解個女人可以覺得自己無錯仲大大聲講畀全世界知？」又有人說：「如果我係男友，一定分手加報警」。<br />\n<br />\n事主疑見輿論一發不可收拾，通過該專頁澄清指：「因為我冇信用卡，本身佢（男友）都畀咗佢卡啲號碼同卡資料我，我唔係喺佢銀包偷卡咁離譜，只係我想入個App時撞密碼搞到佢封鎖咗，我驚得滯先先發制人嬲佢。」如此解釋，你又接唔接受呢？"},{"pid":"3dc61178955c853c83fbfd830154d983ff925096","tid":1080920,"uid":35014,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1a68f90d78666273d9e895b281158db5879c989","tid":1080920,"uid":45788,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"偷竊<br />\n<br />\n拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918ed8091f02f668544c811c808af470e6a1b941","tid":1080920,"uid":117276,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"唔報警都唔撚得啦<br />\n臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1dfb25456cd3dea5396958c31283c38dd2ba8f","tid":1080920,"uid":52459,"like":117,"dislike":2,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFMDToO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFMDToO.png&h=55c2f019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dae43fdc369c632e91f4c0074ee66063d11c8bb0","tid":1080920,"uid":179979,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"條仔呢？<br />\n我屌你老母"},{"pid":"7c4f9df2df38f6e3aa4c7f558992f7d234c371f7","tid":1080920,"uid":240918,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"content farm？"},{"pid":"e7298b02eae8d094b9dbf955a1f940be90b55165","tid":1080920,"uid":838,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"惡人先告狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲一定屌到佢開花"},{"pid":"397b850b8027ebea8a2b452381da2c37efe43c86","tid":1080920,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c1dfb25456cd3dea5396958c31283c38dd2ba8f","tid":1080920,"uid":52459,"like":117,"dislike":2,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFMDToO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFMDToO.png&h=55c2f019&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2104df5690e31d9eed8131e1675bb01c